_header: Ill might he speed where that he go
_description: A book motto of ‘Will. Womyndham Canonicus de Kyrkeby’ — one long couplet

CamTCC1144.Transcription:
Yll mowth he spede where þat he goThat lenyth this boke to
                    frende or foo Amen
CamTCC1144.Note: Written in rubric across top margin as if a running title.
